# ADR rules

Follow template in `docs/adr/README.md`:

- Four-digit prefix, kebab-case slug
- Sections: Status, Date, Context, Decision, Consequences
- Add row to ADR index table in `docs/adr/README.md`
- Supersede old ADRs instead of silently contradicting them
